# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` and populate with your actual values.

```
# Application
NODE_ENV=development
DEBUG=sea-reader:*

# API
API_URL=http://localhost:3000
API_TIMEOUT=30000

# Database (if applicable)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/sea_reader

# Authentication (if applicable)
SESSION_SECRET=generate-a-random-secret-here
JWT_SECRET=generate-another-random-secret

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=info

# Feature Flags
FEATURE_SEARCH=true
FEATURE_COMMENTS=false

# CDN/Storage
CDN_URL=https://cdn.example.com
```

**Do NOT commit `.env.local` to version control.**

See [ENVIRONMENT.md](docs/ENVIRONMENT.md) for full environment configuration documentation.
